nd didn't know any salons. Fresha gave me a whole new list to choose from!`,location:(0,i.__)`Los Angeles, USA`,title:(0,i.__)`Great way to discover new salons`,...si("ciara")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Jonny"),copy:(0,i.__)`Such a sleek and powerful app. I highly recommend booking your appointments on Fresha.`,location:(0,i.__)`Melbourne, Australia`,title:(0,i.__)`Sleek app`,...si("jonny")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Anton"),copy:(0,i.__)`My clients love booking appointments online with Fresha. The consultation forms and free SMS reminders are so convenient.`,location:(0,i.__)`Los Angeles, USA`,title:(0,i.__)`All my clients love it`,...si("anton")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Susan"),copy:(0,i.__)`Love this beauty booking app. There are so many great features to explore. The consultation forms and client reminder texts are great – best of all, it’s free.`,location:(0,i.__)`Brisbane, Australia`,title:(0,i.__)`So many great booking features`,...si("susan")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","S. Derby"),copy:(0,i.__)`Fresha makes it easy to book my salon and beauty appointments anytime I want, rather than having to wait until the salon is open.`,location:(0,i.__)`Melbourne, Australia`,title:(0,i.__)`I can book anytime I want`,...si("sderby")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","C. M."),copy:(0,i.__)`I’ve had four massage treatments with a specialist I found on the Fresha platform. Booking an appointment is very easy – and the massages are brilliant.`,location:(0,i.__)`Gold Coast, Australia`,title:(0,i.__)`Found my go-to masseuse`,...si("cm")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","S."),copy:(0,i.__)`I don’t have to spend ages calling salons to book appointments, I can just instantly book with Fresha! It’s the best salon booking software.`,location:(0,i.__)`Perth, Australia`,title:(0,i.__)`Such a time-saver`,...si("s")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Ivory"),copy:(0,i.__)`I love the concept of this booking app! It’s so easy to browse and find the perfect salons. So glad I discovered it.`,location:(0,i.__)`Auckland, New Zealand`,title:(0,i.__)`Great for finding nail salons near you`,...si("ivory")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Agnesa"),copy:(0,i.__)`Moving to Fresha has been the best decision for my business. My stylists and clients all love the app. It has completely transformed my operation with online bookings, and it’s great that clients can leave a review.`,location:(0,i.__)`Montreal, Canada`,title:(0,i.__)`Ten times better than other apps`,...si("agnesa")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Jess"),copy:(0,i.__)`Absolutely amazing app for booking appointments with salons and spas. Love how easy it is to book at all times of the day/night.`,location:(0,i.__)`Manchester, UK`,title:(0,i.__)`Best app for salons & spas`,...si("jess")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Pamela"),copy:(0,i.__)`Fresha lets you pick the day, time and stylist, gives a price and timeframe for all services on a simple to use menu. Once you make your booking, you get the confirmation right away. Perfect.`,location:(0,i.__)`Dublin, Ireland`,title:(0,i.__)`Hassle-free hair appointment bookings`,...si("pamela")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Jessica"),copy:(0,i.__)`Hands down the best app for online appointment bookings. I can find hundreds of services in my area: beauty, tattoos, hair, nails and so much more. Top stylists too.`,location:(0,i.__)`Dubai, UAE`,title:(0,i.__)`#1 app for salon online bookings`,...si("jessica")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Pat"),copy:(0,i.__)`I can conveniently plan for pedicures any time or day. Works brilliantly. Just wish my hairdresser was also on it!`,location:(0,i.__)`Dublin, Ireland`,title:(0,i.__)`Best for pedicure appointments`,...si("pat")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Kristina"),copy:(0,i.__)`Fresha makes it all easy: finding beauty services nearby, appointment scheduling, canceling, or rescheduling. Straightforward and easy to use app.`,location:(0,i.__)`Riyadh, Saudi Arabia`,title:(0,i.__)`Easy to find local beauty treatments`,...si("kristina")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Antonietta"),copy:(0,i.__)`I love how I can search for salons close to me that I didn't even know existed, and discover new beauty services. Easy to use platform too!`,location:(0,i.__)`Singapore`,title:(0,i.__)`New salons, new services`,...si("antonietta")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Sara"),copy:(0,i.__)`Fresha is so easy to use, with lots of salons and wellness treatments. Good app for quick and easy appointment bookings with local barbershops. The reminders are really useful.`,location:(0,i.__)`St Michael, Barbados`,title:(0,i.__)`Lots of choice`,...si("sara")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Jordan"),copy:(0,i.__)`Great booking app as you can easily book appointments, pay and rate your experience all through this platform.`,location:(0,i.__)`Cape Town, South Africa`,title:(0,i.__)`Everything I need in one place`,...si("jordan")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Emily"),copy:(0,i.__)`Brilliant salon app for discovering new local businesses. Easy to book appointments online and great reminders. I found my new favorite salon on Fresha.`,location:(0,i.__)`New York, USA`,title:(0,i.__)`Found my favorite salon`,...si("emily")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Yuri"),copy:(0,i.__)`I wish everyone in the service beauty industry had this system. So easy and convenient to use. It’s the best salon booking system I've ever used.`,location:(0,i.__)`Vancouver, Canada`,title:(0,i.__)`Great app`,...si("yuri")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Amanda"),copy:(0,i.__)`Easy to use on the go. Once you're signed in, you can book, amend or cancel appointments anytime. Seamless appointment booking!`,location:(0,i.__)`Los Angeles, USA`,title:(0,i.__)`On-the-move appointments`,...si("amanda")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Josie"),copy:(0,i.__)`Love to be able to book online instead of having to ring salons several times. Fresha is a game changer — top app.`,location:(0,i.__)`Chicago, USA`,title:(0,i.__)`Book appointments online directly`,...si("josie")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Kevin"),copy:(0,i.__)`So easy to use and great to find the best salons in my area! Fresha is a great app.`,location:(0,i.__)`Vancouver, Canada`,title:(0,i.__)`Great to find local hairdressers`,...si("kevin")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Nathaniel"),copy:(0,i.__)`This app is great for scheduling and keeping up with my barbers appointments. The best appointment scheduling system I've used.`,location:(0,i.__)`London, UK`,title:(0,i.__)`Barbers in my area`,...si("nathaniel")},{author:(0,i.tS)("Homepage review author","Sylvester"),copy:(0,i.__)`I love the slick and sleek look and feel of this booking software. It’s the best in the industry and I highly recommend it.`,location:(0,i.__)`Melbourne, Australia`,title:(0,i.__)`Sleek look & feel, easy to use`,...si("sylvester")}],[]);return(0,n.jsxs)(n.Fragment,{children:[(0,n.jsx)(b.w.ContentHeader,{headerAs:"h2",header:(0,i.tS)("Homepage section title","Reviews")}),(0,n.jsx)(O.F,{id:"carousel-reviews",numColumns:4,unsafeClassName:(0,j.A)(sn().self,e(sn()["self--refreshed"])),gridClassName:(0,j.A)(sn().self__grid,e(sn()["self__grid--refreshed"])),children:t.map(e=>(0,y.createElement)(ss,{titleAs:"h3",...e,key:e.src}))})]})};var so=s(21445),sl=s(4881);let sd=e=>{let{isLoggedIn:t}=e,{data:s,isLoading:a,mutate:r,optimisticallyRemoveFavourite:o}=(0,e3.j)({isPaused:!t}),l=(0,y.useCallback)(async()=>{await r()},[r]);return a||s?.result.favouritedLocations?.edges.length?(0,n.jsxs)(b.w.Content,{children:[(0,n.jsx)(b.w.ContentHeader,{headerAs:"h2",header:(0,i.tS)("Homepage section title","Favorites"),showSkeleton:a}),s?.result.favouritedLocations?.edges.length?(0,n.jsx)(f.J_,{carouselName:"favourites",locations:s.result.fa